    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 25 article about dressing rooms in boutiques and department stores, which misstated title of book by Betty Halbreich, personal shopper at Bergdorf Goodman</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article last Sunday about dressing rooms in boutiques and department stores misstated the title of a book by Betty Halbreich, a personal shopper at Bergdorf Goodman. It is ''Secrets of a Fashion Therapist,'' not ''Confessions of a Retail Therapist.''</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article last Sunday about dressing rooms in boutiques and department stores misstated the title of a book by Betty Halbreich, a personal shopper at Bergdorf Goodman. It is ''Secrets of a Fashion Therapist,'' not ''Confessions of a Retail Therapist.''</p>
      </block>
